=== Other Structures ===
* Stone statues of the Seven Lucky Gods
* Near the sacred tree behind the main hall, Buddhist statues from the era of syncretism between Shinto and Buddhism are placed.

=== Approach ===
Along the approach is a sacred pond, and on the small central island stand a small shrine of Kogota Yamatsumi Shrine and a stone monument of Konpira Shrine. The first torii gate stands southeast of {{ill|lt=Iwaki-Ōta Station|Q6100384|WD=Q6100384|1=Iwaki-Ōta Station}}, along the tracks of the {{ill|lt=Jōban Line|Q1369263|WD=Q1369263|1=Jōban Line}}.
